snippet.title: TEAM DELUSIONALS DUSTTALE - UNDEREVENT 2024 TRAILER
snippet.description:
We were apart of Underevent 2024, and this was our trailer for the event. It was very nice to work on the trailer and be apart of Underevent this past year! If you haven't watched the event already, go check it out!

UNDEREVENT 2024 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ho5jkOfUFtY
Song - https://soundcloud.com/team-delusional/dusttale-underevent-2024-trailer

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Editting - Octo, Leminade
Music - Leminade, Baughy, Bruhassass
Art - Epickthan, Zalcusidk, Ocas, Satuii, Avary, Candi, Styph, Cereal, Avaheartt, Nik2656, Ellen, Leminade, Imjoniii, Ribimaka
Video/Thumbnail - Avaheartt, with assets from Zalcusidk, Avary, Satuii, and Kass

Team Delusional's DUSTTALE (also known as TD!DUSTTALE) is our own take on the well-known AU: DUSTTALE, which in itself is a fangame of Toby Fox's UNDERTALE.

You will face many new roadblocks as the entirety of the underground questions your motives, and a familiar hooded figure looms over your every move. Will you choose the easy way out this time, or will you strive for a better tomorrow?

UNDEREVENT 2024 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ho5jkOfUFtY&t=3603s
DEVLOG - https://gamejolt.com/p/team-delusional-s-dusttale-underevent-2024-devlog-devlog-6-xjcrax36
SONG - https://soundcloud.com/team-delusional/dusttale-underevent-2024-trailer

GAME PAGE - https://gamejolt.com/games/Team_delusional_dusttale/797156
SOUNDCLOUD -  https://soundcloud.com/team-delusional
DISCORD - https://discord.gg/gMgAQvPzDZ

Tags:
#underevent #2024 #dusttale #sans #undertale #au
